Class CustomerViewAll

    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • com.dinggoapplication.Fragments.CustomerViewAll
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, android.widget.AdapterView.OnItemClickListener

    public class CustomerViewAll
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
implements android.widget.AdapterView.OnItemClickListener
    A fragment representing a list of Items.

    Large screen devices (such as tablets) are supported by replacing the ListView with a GridView.

    Activities containing this fragment MUST implement the CustomerViewAll.OnDealFragmentInteractionListener interface.
